BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:TWiV 1335: TldR\, bacterial hot rods and nullifying norovirus
DTSTART:20260628T122854Z
DTEND:20260628T132854Z
DTSTAMP:20260704T070122Z
UID:8b548dd075800f2c@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:Podcast - TWiV
DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: This Week in Virology]\n\nTWiV explains research sho
 wing how temperate phages enhance bacterial host fitness via RNA-guided fl
 agellar remodelling\, and that IgA antibody is necessary and sufficient to
