DESCRIPTION:WHO will participate in AIDS 2026\, the 26th International AID
 S Conference\, taking place in Rio de Janeiro\, Brazil\, and virtually fro
 m 26–31 July 2026. WHO will present its latest recommendations on HIV an
 d STI prevention\, diagnosis\, treatment and monitoring\, including new gu
