DESCRIPTION:The high-level event “World Hepatitis Day 2026: Breaking dow
 n barriers to accelerate hepatitis elimination” will be convened on Worl
 d Hepatitis Day 2026 to mobilize political leadership\, strengthen partner
 ships\, and advance progress towards ending viral hepatitis as a public he
 alth threat by 2030. Organized by the Government of Brazil and WHO\, the e
 vent will provide a platform for dialogue on expanding access to hepatitis
  prevention\, testing\, and treatment services and addressing barriers tha
 t continue to hinder progress.\n\nEvent URL: https://www.who.int/news-room
